#: ../../source/GamePlayerQuickGuide.rst:3
msgid "游戏玩家快速引导"
msgstr "Quick guide for gamers"

#: ../../source/GamePlayerQuickGuide.rst:5
msgid "如果您是第一次使用Sitwalk进行VR游戏的玩家，完成如下步骤即可使用Sitwalk座椅进行VR游戏："
msgstr "If you are the first time to use Sitwalk to play VR games, complete the following steps:"

#: ../../source/GamePlayerQuickGuide.rst:7
msgid "使用USB线将Sitwalk设备连接到您的Windows个人计算机;"
msgstr "Connect the Sitwalk device to your Windows PC using a USB cable;"

#: ../../source/GamePlayerQuickGuide.rst:8
msgid "按下Sitwalk设备上的电源键，开启电源;"
msgstr "Press the power button on the Sitwalk device to power on;"

#: ../../source/GamePlayerQuickGuide.rst:9
msgid ""
"安装并启动Sitwalk服务端驱动(`下载地址 "
"<https://sourceforge.net/projects/sitwalkwindowsdriver/files/windows_drivers/>`_"
" );"
msgstr ""
"Install and start the Sitwalk server driver(`Download "
"<https://sourceforge.net/projects/sitwalkwindowsdriver/files/windows_drivers/>`_"
" );"


#: ../../source/GamePlayerQuickGuide.rst:10
msgid ""
"进行一次校准( :ref:`calibration-label`)，进行一次设置( :ref:`settings-label`)，启动座椅旋转( "
":ref:`startrotating-label`)；"
msgstr ""
"Perform a calibration( :ref:`calibration-label`)，Perform a setup( :ref:`settings-label`)，Activate seat rotation( "
":ref:`startrotating-label`)；"

#: ../../source/GamePlayerQuickGuide.rst:11
msgid "通过Steam商城搜索并下载安装Sitwalk的Steam插件；"
msgstr "Search and install the Steam driver for Sitwalk through the Steam store"

#: ../../source/GamePlayerQuickGuide.rst:12
msgid "在SteamVR中打开控制器设置，并对要游玩的游戏设置Sitwalk官方提供的绑定，或者自行进行按键绑定设置。"
msgstr "Open the controller settings in SteamVR, and activate the binding provided by Sitwalk for the game you want to play, or set the key binding yourself."

